<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Tandem Run — Find Your Running Partner</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;1,400;1,500;1,600&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/leaflet@1.9.4/dist/leaflet.css"/>
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  :root {
    --ink: #1a1814;
    --ink-soft: #3a3530;
    --ink-muted: #78726a;
    --paper: #f7f3ec;
    --paper-warm: #ede7da;
    --accent: #e8a820;
    --accent-light: #fdf3d4;
    --accent-dark: #b07d0e;
    --navy: #1c3f7a;
    --navy-light: #e8eef8;
    --white: #ffffff;
    --serif: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
    --sans: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
  }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
  body { font-family: var(--sans); background: var(--paper); color: var(--ink); line-height: 1.6; overflow-x: hidden; }

  /* NAV */
  nav {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 1000;
    padding: 1.25rem 2rem;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    background: rgba(247,243,236,0.94); backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(26,24,20,0.08);
  }
  .nav-logo { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 400; color: var(--ink); text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
  .nav-logo span { color: var(--accent); font-style: italic; }
  .nav-cta { background: var(--navy); color: var(--paper); font-family: var(--sans); font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 0.55rem 1.25rem; border: none; border-radius: 2px; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none; transition: background 0.2s; }
  .nav-cta:hover { background: var(--accent); color: var(--ink); }

  /* HERO — map left, text right */
  .hero { min-height: 100vh; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; padding-top: 4.5rem; }

  /* MAP PANEL */
  .hero-map-panel { position: relative; background: #162d5a; overflow: hidden; }
  #boston-map { width: 100%; height: 100%; min-height: 600px; }

  /* Leaflet attribution styling */
  .leaflet-control-attribution { background: rgba(15,14,12,0.7) !important; color: rgba(245,242,236,0.4) !important; font-size: 9px !important; }
  .leaflet-control-attribution a { color: rgba(245,242,236,0.5) !important; }
  .leaflet-control-zoom a { background: rgba(15,14,12,0.85) !important; color: rgba(245,242,236,0.7) !important; border-color: rgba(245,242,236,0.1) !important; }
  .leaflet-control-zoom a:hover { background: rgba(200,82,26,0.8) !important; color: white !important; }

  /* Custom map overlay — proposed run card */
  .map-overlay-card {
    position: absolute; bottom: 5rem; left: 1.5rem; z-index: 500;
    background: rgba(22,45,90,0.92); border: 1px solid rgba(232,168,32,0.4);
    border-radius: 6px; padding: 1rem 1.25rem; min-width: 200px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
  }
  .map-overlay-label { font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(232,168,32,0.9); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .map-overlay-run { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 1rem; font-style: italic; color: rgba(247,243,236,0.95); margin-bottom: 0.2rem; }
  .map-overlay-detail { font-size: 0.75rem; color: rgba(247,243,236,0.5); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .map-overlay-btns { display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; }
  .map-btn-accept { background: var(--accent); color: var(--ink); border: none; font-family: var(--sans); font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 0.35rem 0.75rem; border-radius: 2px; cursor: pointer; }
  .map-btn-suggest { background: transparent; color: rgba(247,243,236,0.45); border: 1px solid rgba(247,243,236,0.15); font-family: var(--sans); font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 0.35rem 0.75rem; border-radius: 2px; cursor: pointer; }

  /* Map stat bar at bottom */
  .map-stats {
    position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 500;
    display: flex; gap: 1px; background: rgba(28,63,122,0.95);
  }
  .map-stat { flex: 1; padding: 0.85rem 1.25rem; border-top: 1px solid rgba(232,168,32,0.2); }
  .map-stat-num { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 300; color: rgba(245,242,236,0.9); letter-spacing: -0.02em; line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 0.2rem; }
  .map-stat-label { font-size: 0.65rem; color: rgba(245,242,236,0.35); letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; }

  /* TEXT PANEL */
  .hero-text-panel {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center;
    padding: 5rem 5vw 5rem 3.5rem;
  }
  .hero-tag { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 1.75rem; }
  .hero-tag::before { content: ''; display: block; width: 28px; height: 1px; background: var(--accent); }
  .hero-headline { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: clamp(2.75rem, 4vw, 5rem); font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.05; letter-spacing: -0.03em; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 1.75rem; }
  .hero-headline em { font-style: italic; color: var(--accent); }
  .hero-sub { font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--ink-soft); line-height: 1.7; max-width: 420px; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; font-weight: 300; }
  .hero-form { display: flex; gap: 0; max-width: 400px; border: 1.5px solid var(--ink); border-radius: 3px; overflow: hidden; background: var(--white); }
  .hero-form input[type="email"] { flex: 1; padding: 0.9rem 1.1rem; border: none; background: transparent; font-family: var(--sans); font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--ink); outline: none; }
  .hero-form input[type="email"]::placeholder { color: var(--ink-muted); }
  .hero-form button { background: var(--ink); color: var(--paper); border: none; padding: 0.9rem 1.25rem; font-family: var(--sans); font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-transform: uppercase; cursor: pointer; transition: background 0.2s; white-space: nowrap; }
  .hero-form button:hover { background: var(--accent); }
  .hero-note { margin-top: 0.9rem; font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--ink-muted); }
  .success-msg { display: none; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; background: var(--accent-light); border: 1.5px solid var(--accent); border-radius: 3px; padding: 0.9rem 1.25rem; max-width: 400px; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--ink); font-weight: 500; }

  /* ANIMATIONS */
  @keyframes fadeUp { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(18px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
  .hero-text-panel > * { opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.65s ease forwards; }
  .hero-tag { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
  .hero-headline { animation-delay: 0.35s; }
  .hero-sub { animation-delay: 0.5s; }
  .hero-form, .success-msg { animation-delay: 0.62s; }
  .hero-note { animation-delay: 0.72s; }

  /* SECTIONS */
  .section { padding: 7rem 5vw; }
  .section-label { font-size: 0.72rem; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--ink-muted); font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }

  /* PROBLEM */
  .problem { background: var(--paper-warm); }
  .problem-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 5rem; align-items: start; margin-top: 3rem; }
  .problem-headline { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 3.25rem); font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.15; letter-spacing: -0.025em; }
  .problem-headline em { font-style: italic; color: var(--accent); }
  .problem-cards { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1px; }
  .problem-card { background: var(--white); padding: 1.5rem 1.75rem; border-left: 3px solid transparent; transition: border-color 0.2s; }
  .problem-card:hover { border-left-color: var(--accent); }
  .problem-card-num { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 0.85rem; font-style: italic; color: var(--ink-muted); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .problem-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; color: var(--ink); }
  .problem-card p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--ink-soft); line-height: 1.6; font-weight: 300; }

  /* HOW */
  .how { background: var(--paper); }
  .how-header { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: end; margin-bottom: 4rem; }
  .how-headline { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 3.25rem); font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.15; letter-spacing: -0.025em; }
  .how-headline em { font-style: italic; color: var(--accent); }
  .how-desc { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--ink-soft); line-height: 1.75; font-weight: 300; padding-bottom: 0.25rem; }
  .how-steps { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 1px; background: rgba(15,14,12,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(15,14,12,0.1); }
  .how-step { background: var(--paper); padding: 2.5rem 2rem; }
  .step-icon { width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--accent-light); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .step-icon svg { width: 18px; height: 18px; }
  .how-step h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .how-step p { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--ink-soft); line-height: 1.65; font-weight: 300; }

  /* WHY */
  .why { background: var(--navy); color: var(--paper); }
  .why .section-label { color: rgba(245,242,236,0.4); }
  .why-headline { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 4vw, 4rem); font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.1; letter-spacing: -0.03em; max-width: 700px; margin-bottom: 4rem; }
  .why-headline em { font-style: italic; color: var(--accent); }
  .why-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr); gap: 2px; }
  .why-card { background: rgba(245,242,236,0.04); border: 1px solid rgba(245,242,236,0.08); padding: 2.5rem 2rem; transition: background 0.25s; }
  .why-card:hover { background: rgba(245,242,236,0.07); }
  .why-card-accent { width: 32px; height: 2px; background: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .why-card h3 { font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--paper); margin-bottom: 0.6rem; }
  .why-card p { font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgba(245,242,236,0.55); line-height: 1.7; font-weight: 300; }

  /* QUOTE */


  /* FOOTER CTA */
  .footer-cta { background: var(--paper-warm); padding: 7rem 5vw; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 5rem; align-items: start; }
  .footer-cta-headline { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 3.5vw, 3.5rem); font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.1; letter-spacing: -0.025em; }
  .footer-cta-headline em { font-style: italic; color: var(--accent); }
  .footer-form { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; min-width: 0; }
  .footer-input-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 0.75rem; }
  .footer-input { padding: 0.875rem 1rem; border: 1.5px solid rgba(15,14,12,0.2); border-radius: 2px; background: var(--white); font-family: var(--sans); font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--ink); outline: none; transition: border-color 0.2s; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; }
  .footer-input:focus { border-color: var(--ink); }
  .footer-input::placeholder { color: var(--ink-muted); }
  .footer-select { padding: 0.875rem 1rem; border: 1.5px solid rgba(15,14,12,0.2); border-radius: 2px; background: var(--white); font-family: var(--sans); font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--ink); outline: none; cursor: pointer; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; }
  .footer-btn { background: var(--ink); color: var(--paper); border: none; padding: 1rem 2rem; font-family: var(--sans); font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase; cursor: pointer; border-radius: 2px; transition: background 0.2s; width: 100%; }
  .footer-btn:hover { background: var(--accent); }
  .footer-privacy { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--ink-muted); text-align: center; }

  /* FOOTER */
  footer { background: var(--navy); color: rgba(247,243,236,0.45); padding: 2.5rem 5vw; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 0.8rem; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1rem; }
  .footer-logo { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 400; color: var(--paper); letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
  .footer-logo span { color: var(--accent); font-style: italic; }

  /* RESPONSIVE */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .hero-map-panel { min-height: 380px; }
    #boston-map { min-height: 380px; }
    .hero-text-panel { padding: 3rem 1.5rem; }
    .problem-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
    .how-header { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; }
    .how-steps { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .why-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .footer-cta { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
    .footer-input-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    nav { padding: 1rem 1.5rem; }
    .section { padding: 5rem 1.5rem; }
    footer { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }
    .map-overlay-card { bottom: 4.5rem; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .how-steps { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .why-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .hero-form { flex-direction: column; border: none; background: transparent; }
    .hero-form input[type="email"] { border: 1.5px solid var(--ink); border-radius: 3px; background: var(--white); padding: 0.85rem 1rem; }
    .hero-form button { border-radius: 3px; padding: 0.85rem 1rem; }
  }

  /* TESTIMONIALS */

  .carousel-wrap { position: relative; overflow: hidden; border-radius: 12px; }
  .carousel-track { display: flex; transition: transform 0.45s cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.2,1); }
  .carousel-slide { min-width: 100%; position: relative; }
  .carousel-slide img { width: 100%; aspect-ratio: 3/4; object-fit: cover; object-position: center center; display: block; }
  .carousel-caption { position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0; padding: 2rem 2.5rem; background: linear-gradient(transparent, rgba(22,45,90,0.7)); }
  .carousel-caption-text { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 1.05rem; font-style: italic; color: rgba(247,243,236,0.95); line-height: 1.5; }
  .carousel-controls { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 1.5rem; margin-top: 1.5rem; }
  .carousel-btn { width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--navy); color: var(--paper); border: none; font-size: 1rem; cursor: pointer; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; transition: background 0.2s; }
  .carousel-btn:hover { background: var(--accent); color: var(--ink); }
  .carousel-dots { display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; }
  .carousel-dot { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; background: rgba(26,24,20,0.2); border: none; cursor: pointer; padding: 0; transition: background 0.2s; }
  .carousel-dot.active { background: var(--accent); }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <a href="#" class="nav-logo">Tandem<span> Run</span></a>
  <a href="#waitlist" class="nav-cta">Join the waitlist</a>
</nav>

<section class="hero">
  <!-- MAP PANEL (left) -->
  <div class="hero-map-panel">
    <div id="boston-map"></div>

    <!-- Proposed run overlay card -->
    <div class="map-overlay-card">
      <div class="map-overlay-label">Proposed run</div>
      <div class="map-overlay-run">Tue 7am · 5.2 miles</div>
      <div class="map-overlay-detail">Easy · Charles River loop · 8:45/mi match</div>
      <div class="map-overlay-btns">
        <button class="map-btn-accept">Accept</button>
        <button class="map-btn-suggest">Suggest edit</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Stats bar at bottom of map -->
    <div class="map-stats">
      <div class="map-stat">
        <div class="map-stat-num">1:1</div>
        <div class="map-stat-label">Always paired</div>
      </div>
      <div class="map-stat">
        <div class="map-stat-num">5+</div>
        <div class="map-stat-label">Match factors</div>
      </div>
      <div class="map-stat">
        <div class="map-stat-num">BOS</div>
        <div class="map-stat-label">Launch city</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- TEXT PANEL (right) -->
  <div class="hero-text-panel">
    <div class="hero-tag">For the girls · Boston · Coming June 2026</div>
    <h1 class="hero-headline">
      Running is better<br>
      <em>as two.</em>
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">
      Tandem Run is a women-only running and walking app — built by women, for women, because safety shouldn't be an afterthought. We match you with one perfect partner near you. Same pace, same schedule, same energy. Not a group. Not a club. Just you and one other gal, moving together, week after week.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-form" id="hero-form-wrap">
      <input type="email" id="hero-email" placeholder="Your email address" autocomplete="email">
      <button onclick="handleSignup('hero')">Reserve my spot</button>
    </div>
    <div class="success-msg" id="hero-success">
      <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><circle cx="8" cy="8" r="7" stroke="#b07d0e" stroke-width="1.5"/><path d="M5 8l2 2 4-4" stroke="#b07d0e" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
      You're on the list — we'll be in touch soon.
    </div>
    <p class="hero-note">Women only · Free to join · Boston launch · No spam, ever</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- PROBLEM -->
<section class="section problem">
  <p class="section-label">The problem</p>
  <div class="problem-grid">
    <div>
      <h2 class="problem-headline">Finding a running partner<br>shouldn't be <em>this hard.</em></h2>
      <div style="margin-top: 2rem;">
  <div class="carousel-wrap">
    <div class="carousel-track" id="carouselTrack">
      <div class="carousel-slide">
        <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Two women celebrating at a race finish line with arms raised" />
        <div class="carousel-caption">
          <p class="carousel-caption-text">"Arms up at the finish line — together."</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-slide">
        <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Two women smiling at the Boston Half Marathon start line" />
        <div class="carousel-caption">
          <p class="carousel-caption-text">"Boston Half Marathon start line. She showed up."</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-slide">
        <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Two women laughing while running a trail race" />
        <div class="carousel-caption">
          <p class="carousel-caption-text">"Mid-race selfie. Obviously."</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-slide">
        <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Two women crossing the New England Half Marathon finish line together" />
        <div class="carousel-caption">
          <p class="carousel-caption-text">"Crossing the finish line together — every time."</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="carousel-controls">
    <button class="carousel-btn" onclick="moveCarousel(-1)" aria-label="Previous">&#8592;</button>
    <div class="carousel-dots">
      <button class="carousel-dot active" onclick="goToSlide(0)"></button>
      <button class="carousel-dot" onclick="goToSlide(1)"></button>
      <button class="carousel-dot" onclick="goToSlide(2)"></button>
      <button class="carousel-dot" onclick="goToSlide(3)"></button>
    </div>
    <button class="carousel-btn" onclick="moveCarousel(1)" aria-label="Next">&#8594;</button>
  </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="problem-cards">
      <div class="problem-card"><h3>Run clubs are too noisy</h3><p>30 people, mixed paces, social chaos. You spend more time making small talk and catching your breath than actually enjoying the run.</p></div>
      <div class="problem-card"><h3>Strava doesn't make plans</h3><p>Strava is a highlight reel, not a calendar. You want to be on that Sunday long run, not just give it kudos.</p></div>
      <div class="problem-card"><h3>Texting friends doesn't scale</h3><p>Your friends are either too fast, too slow, or "I can only do weekends." Why not meet someone new, who aligns with you.</p></div>
      <div class="problem-card"><h3>Solo running has a tax</h3><p>Running alone means doing the mental math — which route, what time, one earbud in just in case. Let us take that stress off your plate.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
<section class="section how">
  <p class="section-label">How it works</p>
  <div class="how-header">
    <h2 class="how-headline">From profile<br>to <em>running together</em><br>in minutes.</h2>
    <p class="how-desc">No more "we should run sometime!" or "come join my run club!". You propose a real run — day, distance, route — she says yes, tweaks it, or suggests another time. It's that easy.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="how-steps">
    <div class="how-step">
      <div class="step-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none"><circle cx="9" cy="6" r="3" stroke="#e8a820" stroke-width="1.5"/><path d="M3 15c0-3.314 2.686-6 6-6s6 2.686 6 6" stroke="#e8a820" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></div>
      <h3>Build your profile</h3><p>Pace range, preferred run types, neighborhood, when you're free, how chatty you like to be.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="how-step">
      <div class="step-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none"><path d="M2 9l4 4 10-8" stroke="#e8a820" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></div>
      <h3>Meet your match</h3><p>We suggest one or two highly compatible runners near you.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="how-step">
