  <h2 class="why-headline"><em>Built by women,</em><br>for women.</h2>
  <div class="why-grid">
    <div class="why-card"><div class="why-card-accent"></div><h3>Women only — by design</h3><p>Every profile is verified. We built it this way from day one because we believe you should never have to think twice about who you're meeting.</p></div>
    <div class="why-card"><div class="why-card-accent"></div><h3>Built by women</h3><p>Tandem Run was built by women who run. We've felt the mental weight of running solo, and appreciated the freedom of running with a partner. We built the app we wished existed.</p></div>
    <div class="why-card"><div class="why-card-accent"></div><h3>Safety first</h3><p>Live location sharing, check-in system, verified profiles, and suggested public meeting points. Every feature was designed with your safety in mind.</p></div>
    <div class="why-card"><div class="why-card-accent"></div><h3>Precision matching</h3><p>Not just pace — we match on run type, schedule, social preference, and consistency level. The difference between a great partner and an awkward one is in the details.</p></div>
    <div class="why-card"><div class="why-card-accent"></div><h3>Truly accessible</h3><p>Built for guide running, wheelchair users, mixed-ability pairs, and anyone who moves differently. Everyone is welcome, at any ability level.</p></div>
